LEAD(cdc_source_commit_date, 1, to_timestamp('31-12-2099','dd-MM-yyyy') ) OVER (PARTITION BY business_key ORDER BY cdc_source_commit_date)
case when dml_ind='D' then null else riskcat_name end
LEAD(cdc_source_commit_date, 1, to_timestamp('31-12-2099','dd-MM-yyyy') ) OVER (PARTITION BY business_key ORDER BY cdc_source_commit_date)
join_filter_column:
CASE WHEN  driver.cdc_source_commit_date >= s1.cdc_source_commit_date 
	  AND driver.cdc_source_commit_date < s1.next_commit_date
	 THEN 1
	 WHEN driver.cdc_source_commit_date < s1.cdc_source_commit_date 
	  AND driver.next_commit_date > s1.cdc_source_commit_date
	 THEN 1
	 ELSE 0 END
